e del Mobile, the Center of the Design Universe" src="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/18kqb57tzg73hjpg/xlarge.jpg"><span></span> </a></div> </div> <a href="http://www.cosmit.it/tool/home.php?s=0,2,67,71,75">Salone del Mobile</a> limped to a close last week, with tons of <a href="http://www.dezeen.com/2013/04/12/to-visit-milan-is-to-experience-the-antithesis-of-design/">shade being thrown</a> at exhibitors by big-name critics who say it's "changed." Yep, the glitziest, most-hyped design week of the year&mdash;informally nicknamed Salone del Marketing&mdash;has definitely changed. Chalk it up to the protracted recession most of Europe is slogging through: <a href="http://www.zaha-hadid.com/architecture/liquid-glacial-table/">$160,000 tables</a> just don't interest people (even rich people!) like they used to. <a href="http://gizmodo.com/5994699/10-inspiring-objects-from-salone-del-mobile-the-center-of-the-design-universe" title="Click here to read more about 10 Inspiring Objects from Salone del Mobile, the Center of the Design Universe">More&nbsp;&raquo;</a> <br><img width="1" height="1" src="http://gizmodo.feedsportal.com/c/34976/f/647164/s/2ac01bb5/mf.gif" border="0"><div><table border="0"><tr><td valign="middle"><a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2F5994699%2F10-inspiring-objects-from-salone-del-mobile-the-center-of-the-design-universe&amp;t=10+Inspiring+Objects+from+Salone+del+Mobile%2C+the+Center+of+the+Design+Universe" target="_blank"><img src="http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png" border="0"></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2F5994699%2F10-inspiring-objects-from-salone-del-mobile-the-center-of-the-design-universe&amp;t=10+Inspiring+Objects+from+Salone+del+Mobile%2C+the+Center+of+the+Design+Universe" target="_blank"><img src="http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png" border="0"></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=htt