 detailing the various online tax prep packages of 1991 should put an end to any of that nonsense. <a href="http://gizmodo.com/5994689/filing-your-taxes-online-was-even-more-terrible-in-1991" title="Click here to read more about Filing Your Taxes Online Was Even More Terrible in 1991">More&nbsp;&raquo;</a> <br><img width="1" height="1" src="http://gizmodo.feedsportal.com/c/34976/f/647164/s/2abf70dd/mf.gif" border="0"><div><table border="0"><tr><td valign="middle"><a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2F5994689%2Ffiling-your-taxes-online-was-even-more-terrible-in-1991&amp;t=Filing+Your+Taxes+Online+Was+Even+More+Terrible+in+1991" target="_blank"><img src="http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png" border="0"></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2F5994689%2Ffiling-your-taxes-online-was-even-more-terrible-in-1991&amp;t=Filing+Your+Taxes+Online+Was+Even+More+Terrible+in+1991" target="_blank"><img src="http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png" border="0"></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2F5994689%2Ffiling-your-taxes-online-was-even-more-terrible-in-1991&amp;t=Filing+Your+Taxes+Online+Was+Even+More+Terrible+in+1991" target="_blank"><img src="http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png" border="0"></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2F5994689%2Ffiling-your-taxes-online-was-even-more-terrible-in-1991&amp;t=Filing+Your+Taxes+Online+Was+Even+More+Terrible+in+1991" target="_blank"><img src="http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png" border="0"></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2F5994689%2Ffiling-your-taxes-online-was-even-more-terrible-in-1991&amp;t=Filing+Your+Taxes+Online+Was+Even+More+Terrible+in+1991" target="_blank"><img src="http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png" border="0"></a></td></